{"type": "article", "id": 26706, "title": "卫星造型的壁灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-12T06:39:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144042wYl9i2EgqxUuOC5P.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">宇宙中的各类天体一直以来都是设计师们的灵感来源，<a href=\"http://www.claessonkoivistorune.se/\" target=\"_blank\">Claesson Koivisto Rune Architects</a> 设计的这款壁灯就参考了 1610 年伽利略发现的木星卫星 IO。它的外壳是一块弯折处理过的压铸铝板，从侧面看好像微微悬浮于墙面上，LED 光源带来的柔和光线则从两端和缝隙中倾泻而出。这个造型独特的灯具还可以通过内置的双重轴线旋转系统沿纵、横轴线同时旋转，自由调节光线的方向。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144040He1qNGgTomR8fnWM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144040yAl5ZdYoNMniEIeh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144041Uyvm6O8JlDjYKa3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144041UlCo2u5bK4XxWIif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}